videos.description: Dwayne Haskins eludes the Northwestern pass rush and throws a 16-yard touchdown pass to Terry McLaurin on the Buckeyes' opening drive.

videos.headline: Haskins evades defenders as Ohio State strikes first

videos.description: Northwestern's John Moten IV finds a hole in the Ohio State defense and sprints up the sideline for a 77-yard touchdown to tie the Buckeyes.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Northwestern RB Moten races 77 yards to the house) 2018/12/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Northwestern RB Moten races 77 yards to the house

videos.description: Ohio State retakes the lead over Northwestern with a 2-yard touchdown run by J.K. Dobbins in the 1st quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ohio State regains lead on Dobbins’ TD) 2018/12/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ohio State regains lead on Dobbins' TD

videos.description: Ohio State's Shaun Wade intercepts Clayton Thorson, then Montre Hartage picks off Dwayne Haskins in the second quarter of the Big Ten Championship.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ohio State, Northwestern trade INTs in 2nd quarter) 2018/12/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ohio State, Northwestern trade INTs in 2nd quarter

videos.description: Dwayne Haskins throws his second touchdown pass to Terry McLaurin near the end of the first half of the Big Ten Championship game vs. Northwestern.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Haskins drops dime for 42-yard TD) 2018/12/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Haskins drops dime for 42-yard TD

videos.description: Dwayne Haskins' pair of touchdown passes to Terry McLaurin give Ohio State a 24-7 halftime lead over Northwestern in the Big Ten Championship.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Ohio State leads Northwestern 24-7 at halftime) 2018/12/01 ESHEET SotFull

videos.headline: Ohio State leads Northwestern 24-7 at halftime

videos.description: Clayton Thorson is flushed to his right and keeps it for an 18-yard touchdown run to cut into Ohio State's lead in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Thorson scrambles for 18-yard TD

videos.description: Clayton Thorson runs the play action and finds Cameron Green wide open for a 2-yard touchdown pass as Northwestern narrows Ohio State's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Northwestern clawing back with short TD pass) 2018/12/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Northwestern clawing back with short TD pass

videos.description: Clayton Thorson's pass deflects off an offensive lineman's helmet and Damon Arnette leaps for an interception in the third quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ball deflects off lineman’s helmet, OSU leaps for INT) 2018/12/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ball deflects off lineman's helmet, OSU leaps for INT

videos.headline: Haskins' 3rd TD pass goes to Olave

videos.description: Northwestern gets a hand on Blake Haubeil's kick in the third quarter, keeping the Wildcats within 10 points of Ohio State.

videos.headline: Northwestern blocks Ohio State's field goal attempt

videos.description: Dwayne Haskins airs out a 63-yard completion to Johnnie Dixon, leading to a 9-yard touchdown pass, Haskins' fourth vs. Northwestern.

videos.headline: Haskins' long ball to Dixon sets up 4th TD pass

videos.description: Dwayne Haskins connects with J.K. Dobbins for a 17-yard touchdown, extending Ohio State's lead over Northwestern in the Big Ten Championship game.
